{
  "stem": "21786.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Also, when you were getting up in the morning, so you had to dust such an orange dust off the blanket, if you were lucky enough to have a blanket, or off your clothing.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now, when they were short of this quota, which they, by the way, increased in 1944, when the Hungarian Jews were coming.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "For about two months, they increased it to 20,000 a day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So they made a selection in the camps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was obvious to everybody what you are selected for.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But we succeeded to let the people who really were sick sick be selected.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I had one experience which was kind of really moving-- when we had been in one of our trips to Israel, so sitting there in the kibbutz and just talking, suddenly appear there two women on the scene.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I got a bear hug.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I was explained, I am looking for you for years.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I know that you were coming here, but I couldn't find you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I says, I can't even place you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I don't know who you are.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He says, I am so and so.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And you saved my life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Saved your life?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How did I do it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, what had happened, obviously, was that I have seen-- we have seen that the SS is coming for to select some of the patients.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I barged in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, kids, out, out, out from here, as quickly as you can!",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Don't ask any questions!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Don't look for anything to put on, just run!",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was one of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Race out of sight.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think they were pretending he was something-- hiding from something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it doesn't make any difference.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
